    <ImplicitInverseRef name="allVoyagesNew" id="170c4fce-4bb6-4185-931d-57c0f00e0362">
        <memberTypeInverse/>
        <type name="CM_VoyageByCodeArrivalDTDict"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>
NOTE: This is an external key dict (hence no inverse) as it
contains the both the "code" and "inwardCode" where the inwardCode
is not null and is different to the code.

It is keyed on the code and the arrival date.

This does NOT include archived voyages.

This has been fixed on 2 May 2008 lets see if it gets dupliactes again by JMT762.
</text>
