Created:			12 March 2001 by cnwdwq1
Purpose:			Called from VB/C++ do show a message box for a query from the DB
Parameters:		None
Returns:			Nothing
Changed On		Changed By		Reason
----------			----------  			--------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*/
